theorem not_squirrel_chases_squirrel : ¬ Chases Squirrel Squirrel :=

  intro H,
  have H1 : Kind Squirrel, from R6 Squirrel H,
  have H2 : Chases Squirrel Squirrel, from R5 Squirrel H1,
